reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really great for a starter desk
reviews.reviewText: I have had this desk for over a week, and everything is still sturdy and complete. The instructions were a little hard to understand because of the pictures. However, once everything was assembled correctly, everything worked out fine. The one issue I do have is the cup holder attachment. It was slightly bent one way, so when I tried to bend it back, the metal snapped off completely, disengaging the holder from the desk. While I didn't get the desk for the cup holder aspect, it would have been nice. In the end, the in-desk outlets are great; they are true to their size and easy to assemble.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Ordered for our son to use in his dorm, it fits well under his lofted bed. It is perfect height, sturdy. We picked it because it can be set up either way which gave us options not knowing which side of the dorm our son would get. He especially appreciates the included outlet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Desk for gaming
reviews.reviewText: This was birthday gift for grandson that was wanting another table for his room to put some of his “stuff” on. Room is rather small. Came across this corner unit and he loves it. My son said a little difficulty in putting it together but is working out nicely. Sturdy, nice quality and now he has more room for his “stuff”!! Happy camper.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars SO EASY TO PUT TOGETHER + SUPER STURDY!
reviews.reviewText: i love this desk. it was very easy for one person to put together. the wood is very solid and thick, and the metal braces and legs are sturdy steel. very well made! it’s also high enough for tall people like me (i’m 5’11”) to comfortably roll under with my desk chair and still have room to spare. i would’ve given it 5 stars if the desk had a drawer. just one. for pens and such. but, the desk is large enough on top to more than allow a pen cup and little dishes of paper clips, etc. — whatever you need to hold tiny items. still, a drawer is always nice. would definitely buy again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Perfect size and was easy putting together since it came with everything I needed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great desk for the $$
reviews.reviewText: Grandson had a gaming desk similar to this on his Amazon Christmas wish list. I looked at similar style desks, and was more impressed with this particular one for the apparently more sturdy construction and a few features, such as the built-in power strip along the top of the desktop. The desk arrived as promised. Grandson was very excited with the desk, and put it together immediately after all the presents were opened. He's happy with the desk. I was happy with the quality of the desk and the price. The company has also impressed me with their followup to assure my satisfaction with the purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Manufacturer sends defective/damaged products
reviews.reviewText: Wanted to update this review the manufacturer has worked with me and refunded money so we can order a new desk.Just received this desk today with 2 bent legs and a cracked top it was damaged before it was ever packaged and shipped now they want me to package this back up ship it back to Amazon and then 3-5 days after they process it I can get a refund to buy a replacement this company is sending garbage out to customers hoping they won't go through the hassle of returning it
